# Task 1 - Write the Ansible configuration file as follows :
	a) The default /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg configuration is overridden by your own ansible.cfg
	b) Configure it to automatically use sudo to switch from local user to root
	c) Also configure it to prompt for sudo password

# Task 2 - Try to ping all hosts by using ping module
	a) ansible <tageted hosts> -m ping
